text: Gay Void as a clown conspiracy.
'Equality' as a euphemism for anonymity is great and worth fighting for. In every other usage it is hideous senselessness.
"January 6" is the calling sign of the Clownworld Putsch. News has been absurd noise ever since. ...
... Secular history is lost. Do something meaningful instead.

TV drama I've lost all interest in:
Dumb but well-meaning Republicans versus sharp and almost incomprehensibly malignant Democrats -- who's going to win?
Imagine how sharp you have to be to get that guy into office, though. (Same with Joe.)
